Future Scope

1) Time Counter in Polling and Debating Section.

2) Multiple Rounds for Debating each round with Time Counter.

3) Published Section:   With Conclusion of completed debates and Polls.

4) Features to be Added: Comments , Replies to comments , like dislike for a particular comment, Report (Much More "Jaise Jaise kuch kuch naaya dimag me aata rhega").

5) Real Time Poll Update wrt the ongoing debate score.

6) For Each opinion their will be two seprate section for 'for' and 'against' guys.

7) Invite Judge.
